  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to demonstrate the influence of peri-operative nutrition on the
      preservation of lean body mass after gastric bypass, as well as it's influence on
      postoperative complications.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Outcome measures:

        -  Lean body mass

        -  Length of hospital stay

        -  Weight loss

        -  Postoperative complications

        -  Cost
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
